&lt;p&gt;According to the question:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6915f54e37dcb4501ea40318.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, &amp;#39;INTO&amp;#39; is coded as &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;5 @ % #&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;प्रश्न के अनुसार:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6915f54e37dcb4501ea40318.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;इस प्रकार, &amp;#39;INTO&amp;#39; को &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;5 @ % #&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; के रूप में कोडित किया गया है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;इसलिए, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 3&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; सही उत्तर है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1) A is the father of B&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6915f2a732f60feafcb65cd6.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) C is the daughter of A&amp;#39;s only brother&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6915f2a832f60feafcb65dda.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Here, B is C&amp;#39;s cousin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage13914.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;दिया गया है:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1) A, B का पिता है&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6915f2a732f60feafcb65cd6.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) C, A के एकमात्र भाई की बेटी है&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage6915f2a832f60feafcb65dda.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;यहाँ, B, C का चचेरा/ममेरा/मौसेरा/फुफेरा भाई/बहन है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;इसलिए, सही उत्तर &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 1&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; है।&lt;/p&gt;

questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;If multiplication = plus, minus = division, plus = multiplication, and division = minus; then calculate the value of the expression:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;18 + 6 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt; 3 - 9 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;divide;&lt;/span&gt; 3 = ?&lt;/p&gt;<br>&lt;p&gt;यदि गुणा = जमा, घटा = भाग, जमा = गुणा, और भाग = घटा; तो व्यंजक का मान ज्ञात कीजिए:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;18 + 6 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; 3 - 9 &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;divide;&lt;/span&gt; 3 = ?&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/04/BODMAS.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 290px; height: 159px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Decoding signs:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); height: 50px; width: 200px;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Given&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
